                             Setup & Installation Instructions

Ensure you have Python 3.10 or 3.11 installed locally

1. Clone the Repository: 
      git clone <your-repo-link>
      cd neurofit-dashboard

2. Set Up a Clean Virtual Environment:
- # Create environment
    python -m venv venv

- # Activate environment (MacOS/Linux)
    source venv/bin/activate

- # Activate environment (Windows)
    venv\Scripts\activate

3. Install Required Dependencies :
   -  pip install -r requirements.txt

4. Run the Edge Application Core :
-  streamlit run app.py

NOTE : The interface will automatically spin up on your local network host, typically at http://localhost:8501.


    
